{"type": "article", "id": 29774, "title": "薯片包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718213414FSnu8qd5R6xIlkaU.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>新西兰厚切薯片品牌 Chip Off The Old Block 最近委托 <a href=\"http://work.phd3.co.nz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">phd3</a> 重新设计了一套包装：为了强调延续了三代的历史以及对原料的重视，采用了卡通风格的工装造型，并且在正面印上了一排不同年龄的农夫操作拖拉机的图案，带给人一种朴实友好的感觉。薯片的口味则通过不同的“衣着”来区分，直观又富有趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213543zAcHt0UiV69BIqnr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213543GXetVx8nEa0JmrWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607182135434dsIwflFPnKerjzC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607182135442t4YbePNyu8I1omw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}